# Liga de Boxeo API Tests
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools
# Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###

### 1. Authentication - Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ligadeboxeo.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### 2. Get All Fighters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fighters?limit=5&page=1

###

### 3. Get Fighters with Photos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fighters/with-photos?limit=20

###

### 4. Get Single Fighter by Slug
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fighters/juan-gonzalez

###

### 5. Get Fighters by Weight Class
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fighters?weightClass=heavyweight&status=active

###

### 6. Get All Events
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/events?status=upcoming

###

### 7. Get Single Event by Slug
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/events/championship-night-2025

###

### 8. Get Single Fight
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fights/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

###

### 9. Update Fight Result (Requires Auth)
# First login and get token, then use it in Authorization header
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/admin/fights/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/result
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "winnerId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439012",
  "method": "KO",
  "finalRound": 3
}

###

### 10. Get All Rankings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rankings

###

### 11. Get Weight Class Rankings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rankings/heavyweight

